data.description: Welcome to 410 W Franklin in the beautiful city of Otsego.  This 4 bedroom 2 and 1/2 bath home has been recently refreshed from top to bottom.  Once you enter you will be immediately greeted by the beautiful wood floors and open main floor.  The large comfortable living area, roomy dining area and the gorgeous  kitchen with stainless steal appliances, granite counter tops and spacious snack bar.   You'll appreciate the generous size of the primary with high ceilings and private bathroom.  This home also features main floor laundry and a half bath for your guests.  Don't miss out the extra large lot this home has that is not common along with a fenced in back yard and a large 2 car attached garage.  Enjoy backyard barbecues or simply a morning coffee out front on the porch.  This home is in close proximity to Otsego Schools rated #1 in Allegan county. Within minutes of everything, this home is a must see.  Call today for your tour of this awesome home!
